snippet.title: Cinematic Trailer | Battle Aces
snippet.description:
Welcome to the world of Battle Aces, a new, fast-paced free-to-play RTS by Uncapped Games. Take on the role of a Battle Ace, an elite commander-mercenary and master of drone combat. Battle across the solar system as human civilization escalates into full-blown interplanetary conflict over resources and territory. 

Get in on the action early and visit https://www.playbattleaces.com to sign up for the Closed Beta! 

Wishlist Battle Aces on Steam today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2682180/

Join the discussion on Discord: https://discord.gg/BattleAces

Follow us on all our social channels: 
Twitter/X ► https://twitter.com/playbattleaces  
YouTube ► https://www.youtube.com/@BattleAces  
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/playbattleaces  
Facebook ► https://facebook.com/BattleAces/

Cinematic Trailer produced by THE LINE:  https://www.youtube.com/@UCJXrkhzPWmj3spakQKvYAiw
